## File Formatting

Files end with newline, no trailing whitespace. See `~/.claude/formatter-reference.md`

## Commit Messages

Use conventional commits (`feat:`, `fix:`, `refactor:`, etc.)

### Co-Authored-By

| Repo Type | Format |
|-----------|--------|
| GitHub | `Co-Authored-By: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>` (all commits) |
| GitLab | Initial: none. Subsequent: `Co-Authored-By: <Character> <email>` |

**GitLab characters**: Match vibe (bug fix → John Wick, delete → Thanos). Vary each commit. See `~/.claude/commit-flair.md`

**Initial commit** = first commit on a branch (even if branch has prior commits from base).

## Secrets (Bitwarden)
- `bw_get_secret "Item Name"` — auto-unlocks via `ensure_bw_session`
- Helpers: zsh (`~/.oh-my-zsh/custom/bitwarden.zsh`), fish (`~/.config/fish/functions/bw_*.fish`)
- Session file `~/.bw_session` stores raw token — shared across zsh and fish
- **Non-interactive shells** (Claude Code): run `export BW_SESSION=$(cat ~/.bw_session)` before `bw` commands
